==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: iron-on
<hw>i"ron-on`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Able to be attached
(to clothing) by applying pressure and heat, as with a hand iron; -- of
cloth items specially made with a glue that is softened by heat; -- used
especially of patches to clothing or accessories to clothing, such as
replacement pockets.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Iron oxide</ent>⟦br⟧
